## Project Structure

- Bridge/
- Composite/
- Decorator/
- Proxy/ (contains `db.json`)


---

### ▶ Bridge Pattern
```bash
cd Bridge
node script.js
```

---

### ▶ Composite Pattern
```bash
cd Composite
node script.js
```

---

### ▶ Decorator Pattern
```bash
cd Decorator
node script.js
```

---

### ▶ Proxy Pattern
```bash
cd Proxy
node script.js
```

---

### ▶ Run JSON Server
```bash
cd Proxy
json-server --watch db.json --port 3000
```

